ABOUT US
Fort Walton Beach Florida
OLD BAY STEAMER
WELCOME
Old Bay Steamer in Fort Walton is an experience of quality steamed seafood, exceptional steaks, and locally-famous ribs. It is also a celebration of great music and eclectic works of art. Join us daily for dinner, evening cocktails and great company.
VISIT THE
OLD LADY
Stop in for a drink and take your picture with the "Old Lady"! Enjoy scrumptious foods and delicious drinks at our bar or have a seat in either dining room. The lady provides good company, and our bartender will make sure you’re taken care of.
